#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:189
msgid "Create bookmarks as shared by default"
msgstr "默认将新书签标记为已分享"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:191
msgid ""
"Sets the default state for the \"Share\" option when creating a new "
"bookmark. Setting this option will make all new bookmarks default to shared. "
"This can be overridden when creating each new bookmark."
msgstr ""
"设置新建书签时「分享」的默认状态。启用后所有新书签默认为已分享，创建时可单独"
"修改。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:197
#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:199
