msgstr "自定义 CSS"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:203
msgid "Allows to add custom CSS to the page."
msgstr "允许向页面添加自定义 CSS。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:217
msgid "Global settings"
msgstr "全局设置"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:224
