msgid "Public shared bookmarks"
msgstr "公开分享书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:202
msgid ""
"The public shared feed does not contain an authentication token and can be "
"shared with other people. Only shows shared bookmarks from users who have "
"explicitly enabled public sharing."
msgstr ""
"公开分享订阅不含认证令牌，可分享给他人。仅显示已启用公开分享用户的已分享书"
"签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:205
msgid "All URLs support the following URL parameters:"
msgstr "所有 URL 支持以下参数："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:208
msgid ""
"A <code>limit</code> parameter for specifying the maximum number of "
"bookmarks to include in the feed. By default, only the latest 100 matching "
"bookmarks are included."
msgstr "<code>limit</code> 参数限制订阅中的书签数量，默认最多 100 条。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:211
msgid ""
"A <code>q</code> URL parameter for specifying a search query. You can get an "
"example by doing a search in the bookmarks view and then copying the "
"parameter from the URL."
msgstr "<code>q</code> 参数指定搜索条件，可在书签页搜索后从 URL 复制。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:214
msgid ""
"An <code>unread</code> parameter for filtering for unread or read bookmarks. "
"Use <code>yes</code> for unread bookmarks and <code>no</code> for read "
"bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<code>unread</code> 参数筛选未读/已读，<code>yes</code> 为未读，<code>no</"
"code> 为已读。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:217
msgid ""
"A <code>shared</code> parameter for filtering for shared or unshared "
"bookmarks. Use <code>yes</code> for shared bookmarks and <code>no</code> for "
"unshared bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<code>shared</code> 参数筛选已分享/未分享，<code>yes</code> 为已分享，"
"<code>no</code> 为未分享。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:222
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Please note that these URLs include an authentication token that should be "
"treated like any other credential. Any party with access to these URLs can "
"read all your bookmarks. If you think that a URL was compromised you can "
"delete the feed token for your user in the <a target=\"_blank\" "
"href=\"%(admin_feed_url)s\">admin panel</a>. After deleting the feed token, "
"new URLs will be generated when you reload this settings page."
msgstr ""
"这些 URL 包含认证令牌，请妥善保管。任何获得 URL 的人均可读取您的书签。若怀疑"
"泄露，可在<a href=\"%(admin_feed_url)s\">管理面板</a>删除订阅令牌，重新加载本"
"页将生成新 URL。"

